  "body": "\r\n***Type***: Bug \r\n\r\n***Summary***: Heavy usage of the app on Android (results of Galaxy Note 4 testing) may result in OOM crashes (`java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: pthread_create (1040KB stack) failed: Try again`).\r\n\r\nIn my case, contact using Galaxy Note 4 device and develop build, used the app for 1h with different activities including navigation from background/foreground or appearing online (~3-4 times) from offline mode. \r\nContact has three 1-1 chat, opened #status public channel, Status Test Dapp, and about ~30 transactions made as a precondition. \r\n\r\nThere are two TF sessions with an app crashes. In both cases, before light UI lags that ended up with the OOM there were: going back online from offline mode OR app opening from background mode activity.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nNo OutOfMemoryErrors.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n`java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: pthread_create (1040KB stack) failed: Try again` on a heavy app usage\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status on Android device similar to Galaxy Note 4\r\n- Use it with regular activities switching between different applications on your device\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: Develop nightly build (439th Jenkins nightly build)\r\n* Operating System: Android 6.0 (Samsung Galaxy Note 4)\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\nTF 1: https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/8473772/sessions/4393825019/?accessToken=ucKyX-k5/X6HQFamE0M3HRqT218\r\nTF 2: https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/8473772/sessions/4393821466/?accessToken=A86qU9hmV5t6ruT3jMLCx6DwFC4\n\n<blockquote><div><strong><a href=\"https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/8473772/sessions/4393825019/?accessToken=ucKyX-k5/X6HQFamE0M3HRqT218\">TestFairy: Status 0.9.19 (6044) @179</a></strong></div></blockquote>\n<blockquote><div><strong><a href=\"https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/8473772/sessions/4393821466/?accessToken=A86qU9hmV5t6ruT3jMLCx6DwFC4\">TestFairy: Status 0.9.19 (6044) @174</a></strong></div></blockquote>",
